    "description": "<h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >《农场与超市模拟器》是一款迷人的模拟游戏，您将在游戏中建造农场，种植有机产品，喂养您的动物，并通过在超市中出售产品来扩大您的业务。[\\/p]<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >种植、收获、使用</h2></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >充分利用您的收获产品：填满超市货架或将其作为动物饲料使用。选择权在您手中！[\\/p]<h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3070880/extras/712613ddd0613d6588c7d221a2dcafdb.poster.avif?t=1759347912\" width=600 height=174 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3070880/extras/712613ddd0613d6588c7d221a2dcafdb.webm?t=1759347912\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3070880/extras/712613ddd0613d6588c7d221a2dcafdb.mp4?t=1759347912\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><strong> </strong>喂养与收获</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong></strong>喂养您的动物并收获奖励！喂鸡一个番茄，收集新鲜鸡蛋，享受劳动成果。[\\/p]<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3070880/extras/8ba366275e2d3ed672f2876474fefe21.poster.avif?t=1759347912\" width=600 height=174 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3070880/extras/8ba366275e2d3ed672f2876474fefe21.webm?t=1759347912\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3070880/extras/8ba366275e2d3ed672f2876474fefe21.mp4?t=1759347912\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><strong></strong>[\\/p]<h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >投资机器</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >通过购买机器扩展您的生产！处理收获的产品，制造超市所需的高价值商品。[\\/p]<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3070880/extras/fcbec3284c7bdcbe05564a2d1795886c.poster.avif?t=1759347912\" width=600 height=174 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3070880/extras/fcbec3284c7bdcbe05564a2d1795886c.webm?t=1759347912\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3070880/extras/fcbec3284c7bdcbe05564a2d1795886c.mp4?t=1759347912\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span>[\\/p]<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >[\\/p]<h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >收银员</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >快速扫描商品，接受现金或信用卡付款，确保顾客对购物体验感到满意！<br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3070880/extras/69d284bb826c99a29b9c6b9578aae2fd.poster.avif?t=1759347912\" width=600 height=174 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3070880/extras/69d284bb826c99a29b9c6b9578aae2fd.webm?t=1759347912\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3070880/extras/69d284bb826c99a29b9c6b9578aae2fd.mp4?t=1759347912\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span>[\\/p]<h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong><br>聪明工作</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >快速将产品箱移至市场，填满货架，并满足客户需求！<strong></strong><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3070880/extras/704cb1bf3819e2accc9583a58467139f.poster.avif?t=1759347912\" width=600 height=174 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3070880/extras/704cb1bf3819e2accc9583a58467139f.webm?t=1759347912\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3070880/extras/704cb1bf3819e2accc9583a58467139f.mp4?t=1759347912\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span>[\\/p]<h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>超市扩展</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >使用赚来的钱扩展您的超市！更多空间、更多商品和更多顾客意味着更多销售。战略性地组织您的货架，突出显示流行商品。<br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3070880/extras/70425e5b910ef9896f812efc6b341a2f.poster.avif?t=1759347912\" width=600 height=174 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3070880/extras/70425e5b910ef9896f812efc6b341a2f.webm?t=1759347912\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3070880/extras/70425e5b910ef9896f812efc6b341a2f.mp4?t=1759347912\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span>[\\/p]<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>农场扩展</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >觉得您的农场太小？那就进一步扩展吧。开垦更多农田，购买新机器，增加动物种类以扩大您的农场。 </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > [\\/p]<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >《农场与超市模拟器》将向您展示管理农场和超市的乐趣。制定您的策略，一步步发展并取得成功。享受这款细致而迷人的游戏体验，成为大型农场和超市连锁店的所有者！[\\/p]</p></p></p></p></p></p></p></p></p></p></p></p>",
